<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Konrad VI., Herr von Bickenbach und Burggraf von Miltenberg</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass er Gilbrecht von Büches sichert und kündigt Bereitschaft zu einem Schiedsgericht in Miltenberg eine Woche vor Johannistag an. Im beigefügten Zettel wird die Zahlung des Botenlohns bestätigt.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_478" id="238v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_478_r1l19"><expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒü Bıckembach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_478_r1l20"><expan>Burgg<ex>ra</ex>ff<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒü <expan>Mıltemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_478_r1l21">Edler <del rend="strikethrough"><expan>h<ex>er</ex></expan></del><expan>lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als Jr vns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt wie Jr von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_478_r1l23"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> geredt habt mit
                            <expan>Gılbreht<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Büchıs / daʒ <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_478_r1l24">nicht vvöll greiffen cʒü vns noch den
                                <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hiecʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_478_r1l25">vnd ſant Johans tag / <add><ab facs="#facs_478_line_1576401053670_1350">vnd <add><ab facs="#facs_478_line_1576401048781_1345"><expan>docʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab></add> cʒü <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan>
</ab><ab facs="#facs_478_line_1576401057889_1355"><expan>gütlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag </ab><ab facs="#facs_478_line_1576401067334_1365"><expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> M<gap reason="illegible"/></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_478_line_1576401063049_1360">gen </ab></add>
</ab><ab facs="#facs_478_line_1576401072118_1370"><expan>Mıltemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab><ab facs="#facs_478_line_1576401075851_1375">gen
                                        <expan>Byſchofſh<ex>eim</ex></expan>
</ab></add> vnd daʒ er die weil ſıcher ſeÿ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_478_r1l28">von vns vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> /
                        danken wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel mit
                            <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_478_r1l30">fleiʒʒe <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> müwe / als Jr
                                <expan>darvnt<ex>er</ex></expan> durch
                            <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> gehabt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_478_r1l33">habt / vnd <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> wol daʒ
                        Jr das <add><ab facs="#facs_478_r1l32">gen vns </ab></add> in güt tüt / vnd
                                <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_478_line_1576400949127_1299">auch das vmb ewr edel cʒü
                        allercʒeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan> / . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_478_r1l37"><expan>Beſund<ex>er</ex></expan> ſo wöllen <add><ab facs="#facs_478_r1l36">wir </ab></add> die ſıcherheit die
                                <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> cʒeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>halt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_478_r1l38">vnd als Jr ſchreibt daʒ vvir einen der
                                <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> der vnſer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_478_r1l39">macht hab / hin ab ſchıcken cʒü ew auf welıchen tag </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_479" id="239r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_479_r1l1">vns das eben ſeÿ <expan>hiecʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        vnd ſant Johans tage / . Alſo vvöllen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_479_r1l2">wir etwen der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> cʒü den ew ſchıck </del> auf den nehſten freÿtag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_479_r1l3">ſchıcken cʒü ew gen <expan>Miltemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
                        / da vvir mainen daʒ ew <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> tag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_479_r1l4"><expan>gelegenlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> ſeÿ / vnd
                        vvöllen ew in den ſachen <expan>lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>volge<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_479_r1l5">yemands <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> / vnd wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel lıeb vnd dinſt
                                <expan>beweıſe<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_479_r1l6"><expan>möcht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Das
                                <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir allcʒeit mit vvıllen
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>Sabb<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_479_r1l7"><expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> vitȷ / Anno xij<hi rend="sup">o</hi> . </ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula"><ab facs="#facs_479_r1l8">Cedula </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_479_r1l9">Auch <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> ij </del> cʒwen guldein / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_478" id="238v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czü
                        Bickembach, <expan>burgg<ex>ra</ex>ff<ex>en</ex></expan> czü
                                <expan>Miltemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler, <expan>lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re,</expan> als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ir von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> geredt habt mit
                            <expan>Gilbreht<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Büchis, daz <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> nicht
                        wöll greiffen czü uns noch den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hieczwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und sant Johans tag <add>und
                                        <add><expan>doczwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add> czü
                                    <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>gütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>gen</add>
<expan>Miltemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> gen
                            <expan>Byschofsh<ex>eim</ex></expan></add> und daz er die weil sicher
                        sey von uns und den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n,</expan> danken wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel mit
                            <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleizze <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        müwe, als ir <expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan> durch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> gehabt habt und
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan> wol, daz ir das <add>gen uns</add> in
                        güt tüt und <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> auch das umb ewr edel czü aller
                        czeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. <expan>Besund<ex>er</ex></expan> so
                        wöllen <add>wir</add> die sicherheit die <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan>
                        czeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>halt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und, als ir schreibt, daz wir einen der
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n,</expan> der unser macht hab, hin ab schicken
                        czü ew, auf welichen tag <pb facs="#facs_479" id="239r"/>uns das eben sey
                        <expan>hieczwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <app><note><q type="date">sant Johans tage</q>24.06.1412</note></app>, also
                        wöllen wir etwen der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <app><note><q type="date">auf den nehsten freytag</q>17.06.1412</note></app>
                        schicken czü ew gen <expan>Miltemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, da wir mainen, daz
                        ew <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> tag <expan>gelegenlich<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        sey, und wöllen ew in den sachen <expan>lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>volge<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> yemands <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan>. Und wo
                        wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel lieb und dinst
                                <expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möcht<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        allczeit mit willen <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne.</expan>
<expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Viti anno xii<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula">
<ab>Cedula<lb/> Auch <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> czwen guldein. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
